Package com.cyberfront.crdt

Class LastWriteWins

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyberfront.crdt.AbstractCRDT
      • com.cyberfront.crdt.OperationTwoSet
        • com.cyberfront.crdt.LastWriteWins
  • public class LastWriteWins
extends OperationTwoSet
    The LastWriteWins class implements a Last Write Wins commutative CRDT. Operations are stored and recalled in time stamp order. There is both an add and remove set, where removing an operation takes precedence over adding. It also contains a list of invalid operations which is used to hold operations which fail during reconstitution of the underlying data element
